task.summary: Adds resizing, changes to gridlayout, adds menubar, adds dragging
Better side panel, adds more buttons
Cleaned a lot, added helper functions, replaced icons
Fixes maximizing over taskbar, adds category creation package, rearranges and pretty-fies some code
Added SimpleMenuBar class, cleaned some code
Added jre and files for jar to exe using launch4j and Inno Setup
Adds Deck and property class. Adds getters and setters for Card and Category. Adds enumeration for loading and saving to file selection window.
Saving creates new json file and checks for an existing file with the same name.
Fixes Jackson dependencies. JSON writes to save file. Deck and Category given getters/setters and fields.
Added save overwriting capability and warning dialog.
Removed some system outputs and comments.
Moved window function listener to separate class.
